reviewText: I gave this as a gift to my mom. It was fun to hear her talk about the places, and what she did in the day. We watch then on Monday nights
Very pleased with the DVD and the timely delivery
I gave this to my Mom as a present because she loves the Eastenders show. She said it was really boring.
I was expecting a documentary about life in the East End, not about the port and it's evolution. Otherwise, it did chronicle the docks growth..
An interesting program that mixes narration with old footage.  If you are a fan of all things British, you will enjoy watching this.
